            <title><![CDATA[【[话筒]#若乳腺结节不疼还增大要警惕#】乳腺癌已成全球第一大恶性肿瘤，发病率从20岁后逐渐上升，45～50岁达到高值。#体检发现乳腺结节该咋办#？医生介绍，绝大...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E8%8B%A5%E4%B9%B3%E8%85%BA%E7%BB%93%E8%8A%82%E4%B8%8D%E7%96%BC%E8%BF%98%E5%A2%9E%E5%A4%A7%E8%A6%81%E8%AD%A6%E6%83%95%23&amp;extparam=%23%E8%8B%A5%E4%B9%B3%E8%85%BA%E7%BB%93%E8%8A%82%E4%B8%8D%E7%96%BC%E8%BF%98%E5%A2%9E%E5%A4%A7%E8%A6%81%E8%AD%A6%E6%83%95%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#若乳腺结节不疼还增大要警惕#</span></a>】乳腺癌已成全球第一大恶性肿瘤，发病率从20岁后逐渐上升，45～50岁达到高值。<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E4%BD%93%E6%A3%80%E5%8F%91%E7%8E%B0%E4%B9%B3%E8%85%BA%E7%BB%93%E8%8A%82%E8%AF%A5%E5%92%8B%E5%8A%9E%23&amp;extparam=%23%E4%BD%93%E6%A3%80%E5%8F%91%E7%8E%B0%E4%B9%B3%E8%85%BA%E7%BB%93%E8%8A%82%E8%AF%A5%E5%92%8B%E5%8A%9E%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#体检发现乳腺结节该咋办#</span></a>？医生介绍，绝大多数乳腺结节是良性的，定期复查即可；但如果发现结节没有疼痛，同时不断增大，就要严格重视。乳腺癌是疗效最佳的实体肿瘤之一，要注重筛查、早发现、早治疗👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a>（央视新闻）<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4961149259546670" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">央视新闻的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/orj480/002TLsr9ly1hj8t8mu889j62bk1b0b2a02.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/Vlxgeus3lx089GaWCyWI01041201oV680E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1698398099&amp;ssig=JwiTu7QUr6&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/wmJlYQPOlx089GaVlN8s01041200IJpj0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1698398099&amp;ssig=f2v6A21ZMV&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/vkMuS1uklx089GaUWWH601041200sqWS0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1698398099&amp;ssig=OW2Zq26z6X&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A4961149259546670" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
