        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[婴幼儿用的面霜一定是最温和、最安全的，#皮肤没问题买几十块婴儿面霜也行#，是吗[疑问]科普来一波[打工人]👇🏻儿童面霜成分简单，功效单一，除了基础的保湿...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[婴幼儿用的面霜一定是最温和、最安全的，<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E7%9A%AE%E8%82%A4%E6%B2%A1%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E4%B9%B0%E5%87%A0%E5%8D%81%E5%9D%97%E5%A9%B4%E5%84%BF%E9%9D%A2%E9%9C%9C%E4%B9%9F%E8%A1%8C%23&amp;extparam=%23%E7%9A%AE%E8%82%A4%E6%B2%A1%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E4%B9%B0%E5%87%A0%E5%8D%81%E5%9D%97%E5%A9%B4%E5%84%BF%E9%9D%A2%E9%9C%9C%E4%B9%9F%E8%A1%8C%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#皮肤没问题买几十块婴儿面霜也行#</span></a>，是吗<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[疑问]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_yiwen-40c066d5c3.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>科普来一波<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[打工人]" src="https://face.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/a1/2023_earner_org.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>👇🏻<br><br>儿童面霜成分简单，功效单一，除了基础的保湿滋润功效以外，几乎没别的作用，如果长期单独使用儿童护肤品，你的脸可能就哦豁了<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[doge]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_doge-be7f768d78.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><br><br><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[并不简单]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_bingbujiandan-9955880b30.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>小卫tips：还是要结合自身的肤质和需求，选择正规、适合自己的护肤品，内心可以是“宝宝”，脸就接受现实吧<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[偷乐]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/lxh/lxh_toule-244c58c525.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫来辟谣#</span></a>（广东药监）<img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hj8pf2espqj20j50f30ut.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
