            <description><![CDATA[<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%A5%B3%E7%94%9F%E5%8D%8A%E5%B9%B4%E5%87%8F%E8%82%A540%E6%96%A4%E6%9F%A5%E5%87%BA%E9%87%8D%E5%BA%A6%E8%84%82%E8%82%AA%E8%82%9D%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%A5%B3%E7%94%9F%E5%8D%8A%E5%B9%B4%E5%87%8F%E8%82%A540%E6%96%A4%E6%9F%A5%E5%87%BA%E9%87%8D%E5%BA%A6%E8%84%82%E8%82%AA%E8%82%9D%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#女生半年减肥40斤查出重度脂肪肝#</span></a><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[费解]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_feijie-c1df37ef03.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>减肥竟会“饿”出脂肪肝？<br><br>摄入减少会导致脂肪代谢所需要的活性氧化酶等缺乏，导致脂肪不能代谢，在肝脏内大量沉积，形成脂肪肝。<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>卫子提醒：大家一定要坚持科学减肥，管住嘴，迈开腿！爱健康，爱自己（爱小卫<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[doge]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_doge-be7f768d78.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> 除了节食减肥，还有哪些原因会造成脂肪肝？👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫来辟谣#</span></a>（央视新闻）<img style="" src="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hj8hywzvyoj20m823ynjj.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hj8hywzyqzj20m820wnkd.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hj8hyx1yh7j20m82357sg.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hj8hyx1i8zj20m82711h7.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hj8hyx1inuj20m820hwz5.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hj8hyx8rryj20m82s07wh.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hj8hyx87ewj20m82ix4qp.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hj8hyx66ezj20m82bde5o.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hj8hyx0xubj20m81ahk6z.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
